        "timestamp": "2019-04-10 20:32:34.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nyou made some changes but you still have csit in front of all the files, and also there is a ton of duplication. csit-customer duplicates create_customer but also adds some useful functionality that others may want to use. Same as service_instance and csit-service-instance.",
